      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh independence study — discretization error quantification",
      "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study on the FDA pump geometry (coarse: 1.2M cells, medium: 4.8M cells, fine: 19.2M cells). GCI-based discretization error for wall shear stress QoI is 3.1% on medium mesh. Medium mesh selected for production runs.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/morrison/evidence/ev-01-mesh-refinement-study",
      "outcome": "Passed",
