      "description": "Particle image velocimetry measurements from the FDA benchmark dataset compared against CFD-predicted velocity magnitude at 12 cross-sectional planes through the pump volute. Mean absolute error 4.7% of bulk velocity; 94% of measurement points within experimental uncertainty band.",
